{"tid":2144602,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"特朗普今日制裁林鄭　葉劉︰全力支持林太","createTime":"2020-08-07T16:27:04.000Z","updateTime":"2020-08-07T16:53:46.000Z","uid":225931,"like":17,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":21,"replies":[{"pid":"1089ffecef19ad41d33a32d50223d7ad94688b07","tid":2144602,"uid":225931,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-07T16:27:04.000Z","msg":"彭博社引述3名知情人士報道，特朗普政府料最早於周五宣布，對特首林鄭月娥在內的中國及香港官員實施制裁。行政會議成員、新民黨葉劉淑儀大問美方，「憑甚麼作出制裁」，假如消息屬實，定全力支持林鄭月娥。<br />\n<br />\n葉劉淑儀表示，美國若然制裁香港官員，是不尊重香港人的表現，她會對此感到憤慨，反問美方有甚麼理由作出制裁，直言美國亦有維護國家安全的法例，作出制裁是「莫須有」的行為，只會讓香港人看到，美國的醜陋真面目，而她作為行會成員，並不擔心遭到制裁，只會對此感到憤怒。"},{"pid":"57b545b9338a9abec71e43eadf0eafce3d2a7436","tid":2144602,"uid":37528,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-07T16:28:09.000Z","msg":"我都支持林太喔，唔好縮<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/upset.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/upset.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/upset.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/upset.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ceca920d94a301f9130df82f9e2fa84be39ae857","tid":2144602,"uid":50386,"like":43,"dislike":0,"score":43,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2020-08-07T16:28:39.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/rKtKCxv.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FrKtKCxv.jpg&h=82178c61&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"6fae557a2000fb52c355bbc25882e86be88e22c3","tid":2144602,"uid":134474,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-07T16:28:40.000Z","msg":"支持妹妹<span class=\"x-small\">去死</span>"},{"pid":"a02909fa8c0d87dead0109ef489d4ed1427e3dff","tid":2144602,"uid":265314,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-07T16:29:11.000Z","msg":"姐姐妹妹我都支持呀！<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a0a81d5bafe2b300dfd31962cc3425717e55a49c","tid":2144602,"uid":335434,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-07T16:29:13.000Z","msg":"全力支持林太<img src=\"/assets/f